":0.58529997,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":0.281,"fifty_two_week_high":3750.0,"fifty_two_week_low":2522.0,"fifty_day_average":3184.968,"two_hundred_day_avg":2958.7974,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":5345.05,"all_time_low":2522.0,"long_business_summary":"Triton Valves Limited manufactures and sells valves, cores and accessories to tire, tube, and original equipment manufacturers in India and internationally. The company offers valves for bicycles, mopeds, motorcycles, scooters, passenger cars, trucks and buses, off-road vehicles, tractors, and aircraft, as well as tubeless valves and valves for TPMS. It also provides curing bag, industrial, and home air conditioner valves; components and valves for CTIS; flash busters; pressure relief valve; aluminum charging valves; and valve caps and accessories, valve extensions, and other products. In addition, the company offers service tools, including core tightening tools, deflation and inflation adaptors, double and single bending tools, electric and pneumatic core runner machines, mold tube connectors, nut tightening machines, screwdriver-type core tighteners, tubeless snap-in valve pullers and pushers, and tire tread depth gauges. It serves various industries, including tire and tube valves, automotive, truck and bus wheels, automotive air conditioning, tire pressure monitoring systems, industrial and home air conditioning, electric vehicles, aerospace and defense, and mining and construction. Triton Valves Limited was incorporated in 1975 and is headquartered in Bengaluru, India."}}